  * fixed memleak in stat-cache
  * fixed infinite loop in mod_cgi
  * fixed alignment crashes on sparc64 and alpha64
  * fixed test system for gentoo ebuild
  * fixed infinite loop in SSL
  * fixed range request for files > 2Gb

